data.description: Beautifully updated historic Queen Anne Victorian home nestled in the mountains of Wallace, Idaho! Perfectly located between both Lookout Pass and Silver Mountain ski resorts, as well as the world-renowned Trail of the Coeur d'Alene's and Hiawatha bike trails. The home is located on a corner lot, close to downtown Wallace and all of the wonderful restaurants, breweries, and shops this quaint little mountain town has to offer. A bonus room in the attic is finished and would make for a great home office, workout, craft, or music room. Great Wallace location for your dream home, second home, or vacation rental!
